resources.string: Hello Instabug awesome user! \n The purpose of this application is to show you the different options for customizing the SDK and how easy it is to integrate it to your existing app

So you want to customize some stuff? While we have default messages for everything that cover 15 languages, we suggest you customize some of these messages to have a more personalized experience for your users! You can also require emails and comments with feedback reports. Everything in here is up to you
